verbose_text: Taken together, our data suggest that SK attenuates glomerular sclerosis and interstitial fibrosis, reduces SCr and BUN levels in rats subjected to 5/6 nephrectomy and abrogates the H 2 O 2 -induced apoptosis of HK-2 cells.
evidence: SK attenuates glomerular sclerosis and interstitial fibrosis, reduces SCr and BUN levels in rats subjected to 5/6 nephrectomy and abrogates the H 2 O 2 -induced apoptosis
